# Summary
This documentation page describes Amplitude Data's Facebook Ads integration, which imports campaign-level metrics (impressions, clicks, spend) as Daily Ad Metrics events. The integration requires proper UTM parameter configuration in Facebook Ads Manager to enable CAC and ROAS calculations, and data is imported daily for the previous calendar day without user-level identifiers.

